graph TD
    A[Complex User Query] --> B[Multi-Query LLM]
    
    subgraph Query Decomposition
    B --> C[Sub-query 1]
    B --> D[Sub-query 2]
    B --> E[Sub-query 3]
    end
    
    subgraph Hybrid Search Engine
    C & D & E --> F[Dense Retrieval: Embeddings/Meaning]
    C & D & E --> G[Sparse Retrieval: BM25/Keywords]
    end
    
    F & G --> H[Aggregate & Deduplicate Documents]
    
    H --> I[Cross-Encoder Re-ranker]
    I -->|Scores Docs against Original Query| J[Top 5 Most Relevant Chunks]
    
    J --> K[Final Answer Generation LLM]
    K --> L[Answer returned to User]
